{"tid":2110642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【投訴師請入】用 老任的法槌 制裁 亂港小精靈圖鑑","createTime":"2020-07-16T05:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T12:19:41.000Z","uid":138409,"like":158,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c3c414264a72d2480dc2cd7eb1c705f7fcde49","tid":2110642,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"前情提要：<br />\n班 藍 屍 整 咗 本 亂 港 小 精 靈 圖 鑑<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2108619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2108619</a><br />\n<br />\n對家開動文宣機器啦<br />\n不過好死唔死走去抄任天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟維穩費定任天堂法務部經費多啲呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n欲知後事如何，有待各位投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qeARvpX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qeARvpX</a><br />\n<span class=\"gold\">電郵地址：</span>noalegal@noa.nintendo.com, legal@nianticlabs.com, customerservice@nintendo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">標題:</span> Illegal Use of Nintendo trademark<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qeARpDX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qeARpDX</a><br />\n<span class=\"gold\">template 1</span>：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>Dear Sirs<br />\n<br />\nI am writing to report an unauthorised use of PIKACHU trademarks owned by Nintendo. It has come to my attention that a Facebook page, named 亂港小精靈, has used PIKACHU and other trademarks owned by Nintendo in their propaganda booklets in which defamatory statements were made against Hong Kong political figures. Screenshots of the mentioned Facebook page are attached herein for your reference.<br />\n<br />\nI note that PIKACHU and other marks are registered at the Hong Kong Trade Mark Registry and protected under the Copyrights Law of Hong Kong. Thus, I wish to seek clarification whether Nintento is affiliated to this Facebook page. If not, please regard this as a friendly reminder of such trademark infringement.<br />\n<br />\nKind regards</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qeARpDX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qeARpDX</a><br />\n<span class=\"gold\">Template 2</span>：<br />\n<blockquote>Dear Sir,<br />\n<br />\nI am writing to report illegal use of Nintendo trademark.<br />\n<br />\nSomeone illegally used the trademark of Pok&eacute;mon. They have printed some political booklet with the picture of Pok&eacute;mon. They also have a Facebook page .(<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PKMonHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPKMonHK%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n39OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=3f0f81ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PKMonHK/</a>)<br />\n<br />\nThey show a strong political stand in the booklet. Without a suitable treatment, the political stand Nintendo may be misunderstood. As I am a fan of Nintendo, I don't hope that the reputation of Nintendo will be influence .<br />\n<br />\nI hope Nintendo will deal with the problem.<br />\n<br />\nYours faithfully,</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己打嘅，跟足老任自己啲使用條款同埋版權警告字眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\">Template 3</span><br />\n<blockquote>Dear Sir or Madam,<br />\n<br />\nI am writing to report a Facebok page &quot;亂港小精靈系列&quot; (@PKMonHK) (<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZuJga2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZuJga2&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n39OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=76442fa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZuJga2</a> ) that allegedly distributes political propaganda mimicking Pok&eacute;mon merchandise, thus violating the copyright policy of Pokemon and Nintendo (<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com/corp/legal.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com%2Fcorp%2Flegal.jsp&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n39OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=c068441b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.com/corp/legal.jsp</a> )<br />\n<br />\nSome examples of the counterfeit provided by the page itself (<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2DQ5HOR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2DQ5HOR&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n39OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=4cb4840e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2DQ5HOR</a> ) clearly depicted pictures and remarks of Hong Kong politicians in a manner similar to Pokemon Go interface. This can mislead the public into believing that Nintendo/Pokemon endorsed its political stance.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sqTfG58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsqTfG58.jpg&h=6d266bc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe Facebook page also sets up a Google form (<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfl5pVlYhpmfCcCUvm11GETrabb_ACpTCLNyjJFCTgeX9E6lw/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfl5pVlYhpmfCcCUvm11GETrabb_ACpTCLNyjJFCTgeX9E6lw%2Fviewform&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n39OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=2b830eec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfl5pVlYhpmfCcCUvm11GETrabb_ACpTCLNyjJFCTgeX9E6lw/viewform</a> ) which harvests or collects the email addresses or other contact information of users for the probable future purpose of sending spam or other commercial messages, as you can see in the screenshot below.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q4BH6xR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ4BH6xR.png&h=dca1a758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAs stated clearly in your company's legal info (<a href=\"https://www.pokemon.com/us/legal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pokemon.com%2Fus%2Flegal%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n39OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=15960503\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pokemon.com/us/legal/</a> ), in no uncertain terms does Pok&eacute;mon's use of Fan Art constitute a grant to Fan Art's creator to use the Pok&eacute;mon intellectual property or Fan Art beyond a personal, noncommercial home use. It is beyond doubt that the use of Pokemon Fan Art as political propaganda does not count as &quot;personal&quot; and &quot;home use&quot;. <br />\n<br />\nInfringement of Nintendo's IP rights hurts not only Nintendo, but also players and the legitimate businesses connected with Nintendo. Counterfeiting is a serious problem not only for Nintendo but also the entire video game industry. It is thus hoped that due action may be taken in response to such blatant piracy.<br />\n<br />\nYours faithfully,</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果有手足識日文，可以去日本官網投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://secure2.nintendo.co.jp/fraud/form.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure2.nintendo.co.jp%2Ffraud%2Fform.html&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n39OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=1e7041dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://secure2.nintendo.co.jp/fraud/form.html</a><br />\n<span class=\"gold\">Template 4</span>:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qeARpkX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qeARpkX</a><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2BmkGi6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2BmkGi6.jpg&h=c8db1d67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PPvxxqN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPPvxxqN.jpg&h=caf81db3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"af9e6f0f0b338766bf91d37950cab853c5031cba","tid":2110642,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:15:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6c8292c839e5aad6516ce276049d053ac99a7777","tid":2110642,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:17:30.000Z","msg":"push"},